Package seng201.islandtradergame.core

Class Item

java.lang.Object
seng201.islandtradergame.core.Item
Direct Known Subclasses:
ShipUpgradeCannon
public class Item
extends java.lang.Object
This class implements an Item which can be bought and sold at the other islands in exchange for money. The items take up space on the ship so the trader must make sure not to buy to much at once.
Author:
Kei Carden
